  "notes": "UK trustee body established by the CMA9 retail-banks ruling. Publishes the UK Open Banking Standard including the Open Banking Read/Write API Specification, Security Profile (FAPI-aligned), and Operational Guidelines. Specifications are freely available; some certification materials are paid/restricted.",
  "wikidata": null,
  "wikipedia": null,
